STATE
v.
OSBORNE 355P18-1 Supreme Court of North Carolina. October 22, 2018 Meghan Adelle Jones, Attorney at Law, for Osborne, Shelley Anne. Alesia Mikhaulauna Balshakova, Teresa M. Postell, Assistant Attorney Generals, for State of North Carolina. Garland N. Yates, District Attorney, for State.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 19th of October 2018 by State of NC for Temporary Stay:

"Motion Allowed by order of the Court in conference, this the 22nd of October 2018."
